{"tid":297074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【收陀地】蝻亞漢踢爛士多雞蛋 警員面前飛拖爆粗兇記者","createTime":"2017-06-25T07:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T13:42:15.000Z","uid":60831,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"611e378e8dda8174da48e6b83d6f2096618fba29","tid":297074,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"葵涌青山公路屏麗徑，早上8時，一名年約40歲蝻亞裔男子，走到上址一間士多，踢爛放在地上擺賣的多排雞蛋，公然向老闆娘表示要收陀地，表明今晚來攞錢，然後離開。<br />\n<br />\n老闆娘報警求助，警員趕至調查，在附近休憩處發現該名蝻亞漢滿身酒氣，被查問時支吾以對，相信是涉案人士，遂採拘捕行動，惟蝻亞漢情緒激動，不斷粗言穢語，大叫「仲乜拉我，依家爭你㗎？」，其間向在場採訪的記者飛拖鞋，警員將他反鎖扣上手銬，勸喻他冷靜，惟他仍不斷反抗，警員將他制服按地，他仍腳踢警員，警員要求增援，等候期間，引來30至40名同鄉圍觀，最後合5警之力將蝻亞漢抬上警車，他涉嫌刑毀被捕帶署。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/d0u5vx8c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd0u5vx8c&h=db0a7fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0xg7nvqm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0xg7nvqm&h=8514054a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同鄉好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548593830c5792826eeb8d73ea781f34481bb7ef","tid":297074,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"D南亞多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f57104c454b7478552a86c1fb8d35c2be95d2ad","tid":297074,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:19:12.000Z","msg":"支那人去立法會收陀地，拉左未"},{"pid":"d25505fa2765fbd1335ceccc31914c7fcbdb0ae5","tid":297074,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:19:27.000Z","msg":"唔講以為張相係中東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成街得南亞冇香港人"},{"pid":"7a5ea8131ddfda1069161923c322cd2eb24b4c07","tid":297074,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0